# .gitignore — TigrinhoDaCopa (Telegram)
# Goal: NEVER leak this project's secrets or local state (see COMPLETION.md §0, §4).
# Note on negations: each `!example` un-ignore MUST come AFTER its ignore pattern,
# otherwise the example file would be re-ignored by a later glob.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Secrets & local config (COMPLETION.md §4: secrets in .env, settings in config.yaml)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
# ...but always track the committed template:
!.env.example

config.yaml
# ...but always track the committed template:
!config.example.yaml

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Database / data (SQLite file + mounted /data volume — never commit, §0 guardrails)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
/data/
data/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ralph loop local state (per-machine loop bookkeeping — not shared)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.claude/.ralph-loop.local.md
.claude/settings.local.json

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
